OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA very windy day with severe
OL,6,Fgales in places. Showery rain through
OL,7,Fthis morning turning heavier and more
OL,8,Fpersistent from the northwest during
OL,9,Fthe course of the afternoon. Generally
OL,10,Fmild, but turning colder in Cumbria
OL,11,Flater.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVery wet and windy this
OL,14,Fevening with clearer skies arriving
OL,15,Fovernight. Turning much colder with
OL,16,Fpatchy frost forming later and a few
OL,17,Fwintry showers. Winds easing briefly,
OL,18,Fthen strengthening later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,166,160,301,260,100,100
